{"tid":814550,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"靜岡一日遊 （行程一問）","createTime":"2018-09-11T10:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T05:31:00.000Z","uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf4c8d364c17868838be60a7eb881db3bad8d39","tid":814550,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"如果朝早搭第一班新幹線<br />\n由東京站落靜岡站<br />\n<br />\n早上去小丸子樂園 跟手行清水魚市場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後行程大家有咩推薦<br />\n我見近近地可以去日本平 久能山東照宮<br />\n<br />\n遠既可以搭船過去伊豆 或者鐵路去三島吊橋<br />\n<br />\n其實我主要想問 由清水過大室山要幾耐<br />\n如果我12點就搭船過伊豆 夠唔夠時間上大室山<br />\n定係安份守己留返係清水市算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08707c5880fe41d1ad7e17535747bad0f9ee404d","tid":814550,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲打去過清水市<br />\n畀一畀意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd88fc240af00a82a98becb9cf82bb49899ad62","tid":814550,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead7f867d8464e0d9a4683d45711a3b7c37ab4f1","tid":814550,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}